channel.description: Hello, iv just spent $30 on my first vps... i went to client.java I made a no-ip account out in my vps ip, and changed it to 'BlahBlah.no-ip.org' well... i put my client up on mediafire and had my friend download it.. it said no response from server. i also changed the ip in gui.java... im using the client that comes with 'teamtorva'...not sure what it was called..anyways, can someone please help asap? i really just want to get this up.. also, i have teamviewer if anyone els does it would be great if you could come on and help me manually.. If not i guess thats fine.. looking forward to reply's . Thank you.
